&lt;li&gt;Investigate market trends and real-time data to analyse, inform, and adapt trading strategies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage risk effectively within the trading portfolio, demonstrating a strong understanding of risk and reward patterns.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proactively research new market opportunities and pricing inefficiencies, utilising data analysis and market microstructure insights.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Optimise trading algorithms and infrastructure to enhance performance and efficiency.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
