&lt;p&gt;Our ideal candidate will have:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2-8 years of trading experience, preferably in cryptocurrency.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Technical Skills: Proficiency in Python and SQL is appreciated but not required.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience trading a diverse range of financial products utilizing advanced trading algorithms.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent oral and written communication skills are necessary for effective internal coordination and client interaction.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong attention to detail.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Decent understanding of options and other financial derivatives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to work diligently and consistently.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comfort with handling financial risk.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
